{
  "message": "test(conformance): add signal processing adversarial cases (+12)\n\nSignal adversarial edge cases (12 cases):\n- convolve_empty_a/b: empty array handling\n- convolve_single_element_both: trivial convolution\n- convolve_with_nan: NaN propagation behavior\n- convolve_with_inf: Infinity handling\n- convolve_kernel_longer_than_signal: inverted length case\n- convolve_valid_mode_empty_result: valid mode edge case\n- correlate_empty_input: empty correlation handling\n- convolve_all_zeros: degenerate input\n- convolve_large_kernel: stress test with long kernel\n- window_bartlett_len_zero: zero-length window\n- window_hamming_len_one: single-element window\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
